1
00:00:04,892 --> 00:00:12,333
When Śrīla Guru Mahārāj
was asked some questions,

2
00:00:13,563 --> 00:00:20,698
actually by the ISKCON artists
who were preparing

3
00:00:20,903 --> 00:00:24,560
[The Devil is in the Details]

4
00:00:25,467 --> 00:00:31,081
to create paintings 
for the Brahma Saṁhitā,

5
00:00:31,112 --> 00:00:37,171
I brought them there and 
introduced them to Guru Mahārāj

6
00:00:37,171 --> 00:00:40,015
and they had 
some questions to ask.

7
00:00:40,015 --> 00:00:41,929
And there are
some mystical descriptions

8
00:00:41,929 --> 00:00:45,526
in the beginning
of the Brahma Saṁhitā,

9
00:00:45,526 --> 00:00:49,991
and they started asking
Śrīla Guru Mahārāj about this

10
00:00:49,991 --> 00:00:54,691
so that they would know
how to paint,

11
00:00:54,743 --> 00:00:57,434
and Guru Mahārāj said, 
“I’m sorry,

12
00:00:57,434 --> 00:01:02,134
but we are forbidden to enter
into those subject matters.”

13
00:01:02,193 --> 00:01:07,722
And then he gave a very extensive talk
about the guidelines,

14
00:01:07,722 --> 00:01:13,053
given by Śrīla Saraswatī Ṭhākur 
in Gauḍīya Maṭh,

15
00:01:13,053 --> 00:01:16,053
on confidential subject matters.

16
00:01:16,053 --> 00:01:21,034
So, I know that the person who’s
asking the question,

17
00:01:21,274 --> 00:01:24,239
they’re referring to something
I said previously,

18
00:01:24,239 --> 00:01:28,026
and so I mentioned what
Śrīla Guru Mahārāj said,

19
00:01:28,026 --> 00:01:33,193
and that’s it—
it’s not something to discuss further
 

20
00:01:33,193 --> 00:01:37,623
or to try and
go into the details of.

21
00:01:37,623 --> 00:01:44,281
We’re not forbidden to know 
that madhura-rasa exists—

22
00:01:44,543 --> 00:01:50,862
the Divine pastimes
of Kṛṣṇa and Rādhārāṇī, Vraja-gopīs …

23
00:01:50,862 --> 00:01:55,192
It’s not that we’re forbidden
to know those things.
 

24
00:01:55,192 --> 00:01:59,636
What is forbidden is to attempt 
to go into the details;

25
00:01:59,636 --> 00:02:05,223
detailed analysis, 
detailed explanation.

26
00:02:05,699 --> 00:02:10,513
Because then, first of all
it’s beyond our adhikār—

27
00:02:10,513 --> 00:02:15,209
our capacity, our eligibility, 
our qualification—

28
00:02:15,209 --> 00:02:26,081
and that ensures that aparādh, offence,
will be committed along the way.

29
00:02:26,445 --> 00:02:36,104
And when it comes to these things,
this is the Supreme Reality.

30
00:02:38,595 --> 00:02:42,972
We don’t want to err.

